Peter Svidler vs Magnus Carlsen
Chess24 5th Anniversary Celebration Match, Game 4, Feb-24-2019 
Sicilian Defense: Closed, Tradtional Line (B23)

1. e4 c5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Nc3 e5 4. Bc4 g6 5. d3 h6 6. Nd2 d6 7. Nf1 Bg7 8. Ne3 Nge7 9. O-O O-O 10. a3 Kh7 11. Ned5 Nxd5 12. Nxd5 f5 13. exf5 Bxf5 14. Bd2 Qd7 15. b4 Be6 16. bxc5 dxc5 17. Ne3 e4 18. Rb1 Bxc4 19. dxc4 Rad8 20. Nd5 Ne5 21. Qe2 Nxc4 22. Qxc4 Qxd5 23. Qxd5 Rxd5 24. Be3 b6 25. a4 Bc3 26. Rfd1 Rfd8 27. Rxd5 Rxd5 28. Kf1 h5 29. Ke2 Kg7 30. Rb3 Ba5 31. Rb5 Bb4 32. Bf4 Kf6 33. Bb8 Rd7 34. Ke3 Rb7

To those of you who read the description: You are an excellent subscriber! :)

Carlsen vs Svidler this Sunday on chess24
This Sunday we celebrate our 5th birthday, but it feels like only yesterday that we launched the website! To celebrate, we'll have several free shows for everyone to enjoy this Sunday, the highlight of which is a match between our star co-worker, Peter Svidler, and World Champion Magnus Carlsen, at 18:00 CET on Sunday.

Read more here https://chess24.com/en/read/news/carlsen-vs-svidler-chess24

Video created by OBS
